# ── Go build / object files ────────────────────────────────────────────────
*.o
*.a
*.so
*.dylib
*.exe
*.exe~
*.dll
*.test
*.out

# ── Coverage / profiling ────────────────────────────────────────────────────
*.cover
coverage.txt
coverage.html
*.prof
*.pprof
__debug_bin*

# ── Go workspace ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
go.work
go.work.sum

# ── Dependency directories (uncomment if vendoring) ─────────────────────────
# /vendor/

# ── Build artifacts (anchored to repo root so nested placeholders survive) ──
/dist/
/build/
/bin/

# ── Credentials / secrets ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
.env
.env.*
*.pem
*.key
*.p12
*.asc
*.gpg
key.json
credentials.json

# ── OS files ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini

# ── IDE / editor ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.idea/
.vscode/
*.swp
*.swo
*~

# ── Agent transient state ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Agent config (.claude/, .codex/, CLAUDE.md, AGENTS.md, …) IS tracked in the
# private repo and stripped at publish time by scripts/sync-to-public.sh.
# Only the ephemeral per-agent worktrees are excluded from version control.
/.claude/worktrees/
